			<div class="content" id="post-content-2067187">
									

<p>Look around you. Strex. Look inside you. Strex. Go to sleep. Strex. Believe in a smiling god. StrexCorp. It is everything.</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Collapsing&nbsp;this&nbsp;until&nbsp;a&nbsp;proper&nbsp;investigation&nbsp;is&nbsp;over</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>Seriously, though, this looks like plagiarism in <em>every way</em>.</p>
<ul>
<li>It's a &quot;smiling god&quot;</li>
<li>It's made of light</li>
<li>It mindrapes people into worshipping it</li>
<li>It forces people to smile all the time</li>
<li>It is painful for at least non-adherents to be around</li>
</ul>
<p>Next thing you know it'll go aggressively corporatist, make technology out of human viscera, and eating the universe. Only thing I can say in it's defense is that it's a sphere instead of being locked in another dimension.</p>
</div>
</div>
