			<div class="content" id="post-content-2353853">
									

<p>Granted, I love the ORIA format and its inner workings as much as the next person. However, the references to Night Vale's Smiling God renders the work somewhat unoriginal. Even if I disregard that bit, the story feels like a traditional &quot;Oh, the horror! The horror!&quot; type of story.</p>
<p>Although I do agree that I like how the djinn react to this Smiling God.</p>
<p>Downvoted overall.</p>

